{"tid":1969972,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"多國大使致函王毅　要求解決廣州非裔人士疑遭歧視事件","createTime":"2020-04-12T20:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T13:05:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":92,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"25d28d02c9a09c949c13249e52a8126c90b4c0a9","tid":1969972,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T20:16:17.000Z","msg":"多個非洲國家的駐華大使致函外長王毅，要求中方解決非裔人士懷疑在廣州被歧視的事件。<br />\n<br />\n多名身處廣州的非洲人表示，他們近期被業主趕走，並要接受多次新冠病毒檢測，但一次結果都不知道，又說在公共場合被歧視。<br />\n<br />\n非洲駐華大使協會在信中提到，這些污名化與歧視行為產生錯誤印象，令人誤以為新冠病毒是非洲人散播，要求中方立即停止對非裔人士強制檢測、隔離及其他非人道待遇。<br />\n<br />\n非盟主席馬哈馬特亦表示，已經召見中國駐非盟使團團長劉豫錫大使，表達嚴重關切。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520308-20200413.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520308-20200413.htm&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=3cd0cb7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520308-20200413.htm&h=2d50dd21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520308-20200413.htm</a>"},{"pid":"58ff753242a87caab2bbed352b541d4d575cd48a","tid":1969972,"uid":201359,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T20:18:12.000Z","msg":"鄰國人真係好鍾意惹是生非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c4f3a84cd5d650dcd9c9e12a7a3f2e9c88e497","tid":1969972,"uid":88743,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T20:18:21.000Z","msg":"非洲國家識玩<br />\n又可以吸人仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99fa9c5c67f51392df2dbedf978362edcab6be59","tid":1969972,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58ff753242a87caab2bbed352b541d4d575cd48a","tid":1969972,"uid":201359,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T20:18:12.000Z","msg":"鄰國人真係好鍾意惹是生非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" cla